title: 847. Bucky's 5 Most Talented Teams
itunes:title: 847. Bucky's 5 Most Talented Teams
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys go through Bucky's list of his 5 most talented teams. For the rest of the show, the pair discuss what you can learn from watching a quarterback in preseason, with a focus on Bears quarterback Justin Fields.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
